column1: # Dataset 3: Phred Reduction Effect on False Positives (Clonal Plasmids
# Source: Figure 1 - false positive counts at different Phred reductions
# "a Phred reduction of seven completely prevented false calls on R9.4.1 pores"
# Starting at ~8.25 false positives at Phred=0

# Interpretation: 73% of variance in false positives explained by Phred reduction
